            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [10 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato base</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
