    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Spread the <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>base</strong> evenly over your <strong>pizza base[s] </strong>with the back of a spoon</p>",
